```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Web Frontend
    participant A as Analytics Service
    participant E as Events Service
    participant S as Storage

    W->>E: Emit user event
    E->>A: Forward event data
    A->>A: Process and enrich event
    A->>S: Store telemetry data
    S-->>A: Storage confirmation
    A-->>E: Processing confirmation
```